cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the issue of unknown offset in non-volatile memories, which is related to error correction and detection in communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.ET (Error-Correcting Codes and Digital Signal Processing for Communication), followed by cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) due to the use of neural networks in the proposed detectors.
